README - test

Last Updates May 31, 2002

------------------------------------------------------------------
About:

This is a test program that is used to simplfy quick-and-dirty tests of the email sending client.
If you run this program it will send a message via email. Right now it is send email to me -> you should change the email address in 'emailer.cpp' and recompile to send it elsewhere.

------------------------------------------------------------------
Notes:
- if you don't have root access you should change the email target to something else in emailer.cpp.

